Schema

ILI9163c
------------
1 LED	--[ 22Ω]-- V3.3
2 SCK   ---------- ESP:GPIO2
3 SDA   --[270Ω]-- ESP:GPIO0
4 A0    ---------- ESP:RXD
5 RESET --[270Ω]-- V3.3
6 CS	---------- ESP:TXD
7 GND	- GND
8 Vcc	- V3.3


ESP8266-01
-------------
    RXD o o Vcc
  GPIO0 o o RST
  GPIO2 o o CH_PD
    GND o o TXD

RXD	---------- ILI:A0
	'-[270Ω]-- FTDI:TXD
GPIO0	--[270Ω]-- ILI:SDA
	'-[270Ω]-- PullDownSwitch -- GND	Flash button
GPIO2	---------- ILI:SCK
GND	- GND
Vcc	- V3.3
RST	--[270Ω]-- PullDownSwitch -- GND	Reset button
CH_PD	--[10kΩ]-- V3.3
TXD	---------- ILI:CS
	'-[270Ω]-- FTDI:RXD


FTDI
-----
DTR	-o
RXD	--[270Ω]-- ESP:TXD
TXD	--[270Ω]-- ESP:RXD
Vcc	- PullDown:In	(5V!)
CTS	- GND
GND	- GND

FTDI 3.3V out is not strong enough to power the ESP8266. Check RXD and TXD to be at 3.3V level.


PullDown 5V to 3.3V
--------------------
GND	- GND
Vout	- V3.3
Vin	- FTDI:Vcc (5V)
